OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPM: 'It looks like P&O mass
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsackings broke the law'    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, P&O Ferries' decision to sack 800      
OL,6, workers without notice last week       
OL,7, appears to have broken UK employment   
OL,8, law, the prime minister has said.      
OL,10,FThe firm could face fines "running into
OL,11,Fmillions of pounds" if found guilty,   
OL,12,FBoris Johnson told the House of        
OL,13,FCommons.                               
OL,15,FIt came as the boss of P&O Ferries     
OL,16,Fapologised for the mass sacking.       
OL,18,FPeter Hebblethwaite said the decision  
OL,19,Fwas "incredibly difficult" but "the    
OL,20,Fonly way to save the business".        
